\c 5
\s Ukusokwa kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi lapho wonke amakhosi amaAmori ayenganeno kweJordani ngentshonalanga lawo wonke amakhosi amaKhanani ayengaselwandle\x + Nani 13.29.\x* esizwa ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza amanzi eJordani atsha ngaphambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 15.14.\x* saze sachapha, inhliziyo yawo yancibilika\x + 2.11.\x*, kakusabanga khona moya kiwo, ngenxa yabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 1 Kho. 10.5. Josh. 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Ngalesosikhathi iN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kuJoshuwa: Zenzele ingqamu zensengetshe, ubasoke futhi abantwana bakoIsrayeli okwesibili.
\v 3 UJoshuwa wasezenzela ingqamu zensengetshe, wabasoka abantwana bakoIsrayeli oqaqeni lwamajwabu aphambili.
\v 4 Njalo yilesisizatho uJoshuwa a\add ba\add*sokela sona; bonke abantu abaphuma eGibhithe, abesilisa, amadoda wonke empi, afela enkangala endleleni esephumile eGibhithe\x + Nani 14.29. 26.64,65. Dute. 2.16.\x*.
\v 5 Ngoba bonke abantu abaphumayo babesokiwe, kodwa bonke abantu ababezalelwe enkangala endleleni sebephumile eGibhithe babengabasokanga.
\v 6 Ngoba abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahamba enkangala iminyaka engamatshumi amane saze sabhubha isizwe sonke samadoda empi ayephume eGibhithe, ngoba engalilalelanga ilizwi leN\nd kosi\x + Nani 14.33. Dute. 1.3. 2.7,14. Hlab. 95.10.\x*\nd*; iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayifungile kuwo ukuthi kayiyikuwatshengisa ilizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayifungele oyise ukusinika lona\x + Nani 14.23. Hlab. 95.11. Heb. 3.11.\x*, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju\x + Eks. 3.8.\x*.
\v 7 Labantwana bawo yabavusa esikhundleni sawo; bona uJoshuwa wabasoka, ngoba babengasokwanga, ngoba babengabasokanga endleleni\x + Nani 14.31. Dute. 1.39.\x*.
\v 8 Kwasekusithi sebeqedile ukusoka isizwe sonke, bahlala endaweni yabo enkambeni baze baphola\x + Gen. 34.25.\x*.
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuJoshuwa: Lamuhla ngigiqile ngasusa kini ihlazo leGibhithe\x + Gen. 34.14.\x*. Ngakho ibizo laleyondawo lathiwa yiGiligali kuze kube lamuhla\x + 4.19.\x*.
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli bagcina iphasika eGiligali
\p
\v 10 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebemisa inkamba eGiligali, bagcina iphasika ngosuku lwetshumi lane lwenyanga kusihlwa emagcekeni eJeriko\x + Eks. 12.6. Josh. 4.19. 4.8.\x*.
\v 11 Basebesidla izithelo zelizwe, ngekuseni eyalandela iphasika, izinkwa ezingelamvubelo lamabele akhanzingiweyo, ngalona lolosuku\x + Levi 2.14.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Imana yacina ngelanga elalandela abadla ngalo izithelo zelizwe; labantwana bakoIsrayeli kabasabanga lemana, kodwa badla izithelo zelizwe leKhanani ngalowomnyaka\x + Eks. 16.35.\x*.
\s Induna lebutho leN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 13 Kwasekusithi uJoshuwa eseJeriko, waphakamisa amehlo akhe wabona, khangela-ke, indoda imi maqondana laye\x + Gen. 18.2. 32.24. Zek. 1.8-11. Seb. 1.10. Eks. 23.20,23.\x* ilenkemba yayo ehwatshiweyo isesandleni sayo\x + Nani 22.23.\x*. UJoshuwa wasesiya kuyo wathi kuyo: Ungowakithi yini, kumbe ungowezitha zethu?
\v 14 Wasesithi: Hatshi; kodwa ngiyinduna yebutho leN\nd kosi\nd*; sengibuyile. UJoshuwa wasesithi mbo ngobuso bakhe emhlabathini, wakhonza esithi kuye: INkosi yami ithini encekwini yayo\x + Gen. 17.3.\x*?
\v 15 Induna yebutho leN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuJoshuwa: Khulula inyathela lakho enyaweni lwakho, ngoba indawo omi kiyo ingcwele. UJoshuwa wasesenza njalo\x + Eks. 3.5. Seb. 7.33.\x*.
